    "author": "Matt",
    "description": "A gnome's infernal machine blocks the sun, plunging the town of Duskhollow into perpetual darkness. The guild of tinkerers has failed to stop it. Now a band of adventurers must recover the 8 Keys of the Gnomes from increasingly dangerous dungeons and shut down the machine to restore sunlight.",
